  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Substance of Concern (SoC) inspection event referencing the product's",
    "4-type SoC classification per ESPR Article 7(5).",
    "Substance composition is a property of the product (the dye, finish and",
    "fluorocarbon chemistry are inherent to the SKU), so substancesOfConcern",
    "lives INSIDE masterDataAvailableFor on the product entry. The event",
    "itself records WHEN and WHERE the inspection happened.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,textile=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/textile/",
    "See: core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
